Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.publishing.common.ncf.contracts

classes representing NCF contracts.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IContractProvider A contract provider manages the service contract models.
 

Class Summary
ArrayType A model for one-dimensional array types that are used by a service contract.
DataContract The model for complex data types that are used in service contracts as arguments and return values of method calls.
DataType Abstract base class of all data types in the contract model.
EnumType A model for enumeration data types used by a service contract.
MethodContract A platform-independent model for a method signature.
Property A model for a property that is part of a data contract.
ServiceContract Platform-independent model of a service contract.
SimpleType Represents a simple type defined by SimpleTypeKind.
 

Enum Summary
SimpleTypeKind The set of simple types known by the contract model.
 

Exception Summary
ContractException Exception thrown when problems with the contract model occur.
